{"tid":2233801,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"諾貝爾醫學獎及化學獎得主曾獲李嘉誠捐助，基金會：李生高興落淚","createTime":"2020-10-07T11:44:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T13:27:24.000Z","uid":1886,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bf24fa39473bdcdb03cdb1fd00a653c6944f3a0c","tid":2233801,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:44:33.000Z","msg":"今年諾貝爾獎得主陸續揭曉，其中諾貝爾醫學獎及化學獎得主與李嘉誠甚有淵源，諾貝爾醫學獎得主英國科學家霍頓（Michael Houghton）及化學獎得主美國科學家道納（Jennifer Doudna）同為李嘉誠基金會捐助的研究所教授，基金會表示，衷心恭賀兩位得獎，李嘉誠得知消息後高興得淚下， 相信二人的科研方向，並分別於2010年及2011年支持二人工作，感謝他們及團隊的努力，為世界帶來改變和希望。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201007/OA2PPVJBOZDJXPWR2VOH7BIJBE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201007%2FOA2PPVJBOZDJXPWR2VOH7BIJBE%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=67694798\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201007%2FOA2PPVJBOZDJXPWR2VOH7BIJBE%2F&h=4de008f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201007/OA2PPVJBOZDJXPWR2VOH7BIJBE/</a>"},{"pid":"333be744107d211919525239549d93429f7b1897","tid":2233801,"uid":49532,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:46:06.000Z","msg":"誠哥:哭𠹌咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1754827bb218cae50894a2294f60602a2e183ea","tid":2233801,"uid":366655,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:52:21.000Z","msg":"誠哥間接造福世人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ac57774f63b134739e0189b501c55a9c574d14","tid":2233801,"uid":263944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:57:54.000Z","msg":"誠歌又贏"},{"pid":"8803d08b09793ba70c471fbddc48c47e5c5d8cd6","tid":2233801,"uid":49336,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:59:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d